data.title: GRI Corporate Brochure 2008
data.meta_description: GRI Corporate Brochure 2008 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information about upcoming real estate industry events organized by the Global Real Estate Institute (GRI) in 2007-2008. The GRI is described as a global club for senior real estate investors, developers, and lenders. The GRI aims to help members build relationships and create business opportunities through regional meetings that bring together high-level real estate executives. Upcoming meetings include events in London, Frankfurt, Beijing, Paris, Moscow, New Delhi, Istanbul, Dubai, and St. Moritz.
